    <div class="pr-strategy">
      <div class="pr-tip"><span class="pr-tip__icon">🎯</span><div><p class="pr-tip__title">Elimination Technique</p><p class="pr-tip__desc">With -0.66 negative marking, attempt only when you can eliminate 2+ options. Random guessing costs marks.</p></div></div>
      <div class="pr-tip"><span class="pr-tip__icon">🏆</span><div><p class="pr-tip__title">Target: 90+ correct, &lt;15 wrong</p><p class="pr-tip__desc">That gives ~110/200 net — above most cutoffs. Track accuracy per subject to find weak areas.</p></div></div>
