      <div class="pr-tip"><span class="pr-tip__icon">📰</span><div><p class="pr-tip__title">Current Affairs = 30-40%</p><p class="pr-tip__desc">Daily <a href="https://ujiyari.com/daily/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ujiyari.com</a> + monthly compilations. Static topics are often framed through recent events.</p></div></div>
